(94, 1, '2020-10-12 07:14:54', '2020-10-12 07:14:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This year, we’re continuing to build on powerful automation and guided editing features you’ve come to expect from Photoshop Elements and Premiere Elements. Leveraging Adobe Sensei AI technology, we’re streamlining organization and editing capabilities for both veteran and novice Elements users.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Today the Elements team is excited to announce the release of Photoshop Elements 2021 &amp; Premiere Elements 2021. This latest release makes it even easier for you to follow your creative inspiration where it leads.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Introducing Adobe Photoshop Elements 2021 & Premiere Elements 2021', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'introducing-adobe-photoshop-elements-2021-premiere-elements-2021', '', '', '2020-10-12 07:15:51', '2020-10-12 07:15:51', '', 0, 'http://server.visionvivante.com:8080/review_system/blog/?p=94', 0, 'post', '', 0),
